    {"type": "text", "id": "dc_t2", "x": 1090, "y": 420, "width": 300, "height": 210,
     "text": "$TMPDIR/go-viz-cache/<id>/\n├ parsed.gob  (encoding/gob)\n├ graph.json\n├ deadcode.json\n└ meta.json (mtime, TTL)\n\nsurvives server restart\n\nTTL 1h idle · sweeper goroutine\nGC expired project dirs\n\nsingle-flight per project\n(sync.Map of *sync.Mutex)",
