     "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25},
    {"type": "text", "id": "deps_t2", "x": 1490, "y": 250, "width": 260, "height": 400,
     "text": "stdlib:\n  net/http\n  archive/zip\n  encoding/json, encoding/gob\n  embed\n  go/ast, go/types, go/token\n  sync, sync/atomic\n  os, io/fs, path/filepath\n  context, time, log/slog\n\ngolang.org/x/tools:\n  go/packages (typed load)\n  go/types/typeutil\n\nno framework:\nno chi, no gin, no echo —\npure stdlib net/http routing",
     "originalText": "stdlib:\n  net/http\n  archive/zip\n  encoding/json, encoding/gob\n  embed\n  go/ast, go/types, go/token\n  sync, sync/atomic\n  os, io/fs, path/filepath\n  context, time, log/slog\n\ngolang.org/x/tools:\n  go/packages (typed load)\n  go/types/typeutil\n\nno framework:\nno chi, no gin, no echo —\npure stdlib net/http routing",
     "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
     "strokeColor": "#374151", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
