    {"type": "text", "id": "jm_t2", "x": 150, "y": 745, "width": 860, "height": 80,
     "text": "wires pipeline together · drives per-analysis goroutine · propagates context.Context (cancellation, deadlines)\nstreams phase events into SSEStreamer · recovers panics · single-flight per project_id\nreads entry_points + filters from request, delegates to EntryPointsResolver + ReachabilityAnalyzer",
     "originalText": "wires pipeline together · drives per-analysis goroutine · propagates context.Context (cancellation, deadlines)\nstreams phase events into SSEStreamer · recovers panics · single-flight per project_id\nreads entry_points + filters from request, delegates to EntryPointsResolver + ReachabilityAnalyzer",
     "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
